+     * case size to byte length
+     * example:
+     *   2k => 2 * 1024
+     *   2m => 2 * 1024 * 1024
+     *   2g => 2 * 1024 * 1024 * 1024
+     *   2t => 2 * 1024 * 1024 * 1024 * 1024
+     * @param size the string size with unit
+     * @return the byte length
